{"tid":1167403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國新增13中國企業制裁","createTime":"2019-05-23T04:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T01:40:06.000Z","uid":52763,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"01b1db148e3dcd70e325e21100372a783563f144","tid":1167403,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"美國國務院國際安全與防擴散局（Bureau of International Security and Nonproliferation）宣佈對13個中國企業及個人實施制裁，其中包括友祥科技、浙江兆晨科技等10家企業以及3名個人，聲明要求任何美國政府部門不得向這些企業或個人採購任何服務、產品、技術，不得與這些人員訂立任何服務、產品、技術採購合同，不得向這些企業與人員提供任何協助，暫停授予這些人員現有的所有許可。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190523/59631682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F59631682&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=292bc934\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F59631682&h=083d1397\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190523/59631682</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20e7e0554f4a60cf5b9b67fc97073b6714cde6e","tid":1167403,"uid":52763,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"13間中國企業及個人包括： <br />\nAbaseience Tech Co.,Ltd.（China）及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\nEmily Liu（又名Emily Lau, Liu Baoxial）<br />\nHope Wish Technologies Incorporated（China）及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\nJiangsu Tianyuan Metal Powder Co Ltd（China）（江蘇天元金屬粉末有限公司）及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\nLi Fangwei（又名Karl Lee）<br />\nRaybeam Optronics Co., Ltd（China）及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\nRuan Runling（又名Ricky Runling、Ricky Ruan）<br />\nShanghai North Begins（China）及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\nSinotech（Dalian）Carbon and Graphite Corporation（SCGC）（China）（中國科技碳石墨製造總公司（大連））及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\nSun Creative Zhejiang Technologies Inc（China）（浙江兆晨科技股份有限公司）及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\nT-Rubber Co. Ltd（China）及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\nWuhan Sanjiang Import and Export Co Ltd（China）及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\nYenben Yansong Zaojiu Co Ltd（China）及其任何繼承人、分支機構、子公司<br />\n<br />\n美國的制裁措施包括： <br />\n除非美國國務院另行決定，任何美國政府部門不得向上述外國人員採購任何服務、產品、技術，或與這些人員訂立任何服務、產品、技術採購合同；<br />\n除非美國國務院另行決定，任何美國政府部門不得向這些人員提供任何協助，這些人員也不能參與由美國政府提供協助的任何活動；<br />\n任何美國政府不得向這些人員銷售任何軍品清單上的物品，並終止向這些人員銷售任何美國《武器出口管制法》管控的國防物品、國防服務或設計和施工服務；<br />\n不得就任何受EAA或EAR管控物品的出口向這些人員頒佈新的個別許可，並暫停授予這些人員現有的任何許可。"},{"pid":"be50c611273a11a6dd2ba30968116de6c24e4ffd","tid":1167403,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"美帝又出拳了，習帝要亮劍吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3922fd6c410bf42a345af71dabc22ac239dcbc","tid":1167403,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"美國公開處刑（公布失信中國企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n方式和力度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都比中國更牛B<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/09/%E9%AB%98%E9%93%81-%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8-20180905190733_101a_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F09%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2593%2581-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%2594%25A8-20180905190733_101a_large.png&h=e5ebe5b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a9a6bf70312e0c6adaff2c4631f67f573e8ca57","tid":1167403,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cQQOKi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cQQOKi.gif&h=421cc739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日咁high 美帝畀我停下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ba86836275004ade995f730189af7ba79c9ad6","tid":1167403,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dece2e9fc44d67fbbe2045323b67ae42ca7bcfe","tid":1167403,"uid":33908,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:49:33.000Z","msg":"睇個英文名..似又係有香港身分證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09314ee5cf62308b2c17d3dd6c9f2bab9fb7678","tid":1167403,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"30ba86836275004ade995f730189af7ba79c9ad6","tid":1167403,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"你有冇留意恆指日日跌緊？<br />\n過多排就到地產狗失業 再過多排保險狗 之後就到建築零售 係慢慢燒落去既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2436ee0079878322464a2b6337d01aca4181aee4","tid":1167403,"uid":60686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:00:49.000Z","msg":"D 姓又要扮哂香港人既英文拼音，好撚嘔心"},{"pid":"aa4985a4e02e97be8530fdb3d15c586c6db4aa1d","tid":1167403,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}